{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act34side_level_act34side_07_beg","storyGroup":"act34side","storySort":15,"storyDependence":"act34side_level_act34side_st02","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BP-7","storyName":"从历史中来","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"海嗣侵入信标塔，城市异变陡生。克莱门莎执政官组织全城应对灾变，护送博士与凯尔希去往港口，却在途中遭遇了未曾设想的敌人——已经海嗣化的阿戈尔人，数百年前失踪的先史文明研究者。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act34side/level_act34side_07_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act34side_07","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":13,"next":15,"characters":["紧张的阿戈尔人","神秘的阿戈尔人","？？？","西昆妲","海巡队队长","克莱门莎","凯尔希","乔迪","乌尔比安","设施管理所的“小帮手”","阿维图斯","“小帮手”","Mon3tr","神秘的海嗣","“海嗣”"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"charslot","id":5},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_deepseaamb","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"u","id":6},{"type":"text","text":"总有铃铛般的乐声从穹顶上传来，那是无数须腕状的生物监测单元在解析海流最微小的动向。","id":7},{"type":"text","text":"港口处时而传来隐隐的钝响，出港或是返航的舰船如同庞大的鳞，优雅地破开万钧海水。","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"压缩态的物资顺着半空中的光缆进入千家万户，它们流淌时传出细微的嗡鸣。","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"万千声响，繁多而不杂乱，居住在弥利亚留姆的十余万军民，早已熟悉这座孤城的声音。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"但所有人都在此刻停了下来，怀疑起自己的耳朵。","id":12},{"type":"dialog","id":13},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"u","fadetime":"2","id":14},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"0.3","fadetime":"0.1","id":15},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"0.3","fadetime":"0.1","id":16},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_bat_act17side_03_intro","volume":"0.6","id":17,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":18},{"type":"background","y":"60","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","screenadapt":"coverall","id":19},{"type":"backgroundtween","xFrom":"170","xTo":"-170","duration":"30","block":"false","id":20},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":21},{"type":"text","text":"起初，仿佛只是一缕风掠过礁石的夹角。","id":22},{"type":"text","text":"继而，一只幼小的生命从母胎的温暖中探出脑袋。","id":23},{"type":"text","text":"紧接着，是一个群体、一个巢穴、一片海域。","id":24},{"type":"dialog","id":25},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.3","fillto":"0","fadetime":"4","id":26},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.3","fillto":"0","fadetime":"4","id":27},{"type":"background","xScale":"1.05","yScale":"1.05","fadetime":"2","screenadapt":"coverall","id":28},{"type":"backgroundtween","xScaleFrom":"1.05","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleFrom":"1.05","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"10","block":"false","id":29},{"type":"delay","time":"4","id":30},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_ropytissuegrow","volume":"1","id":31},{"type":"background","fadetime":"4","screenadapt":"coverall","id":32},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":33},{"type":"text","text":"......生命集中绽放的异响，清晰可闻。","id":34},{"type":"text","text":"海的子嗣反哺海洋。","id":35},{"type":"text","text":"它吻过文明，于是文明变得愈发生机盎然。","id":36},{"type":"dialog","id":37},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_emgseaalarm","volume":"1","id":38},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.2","r":"0.92","g":"0.4","b":"0.3","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":39},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0.92","g":"0.4","b":"0.3","fadetime":"0.4","block":"true","id":40},{"type":"delay","time":"0.4","id":41},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_emgseaalarm","volume":"1","id":42},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.2","r":"0.92","g":"0.4","b":"0.3","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":43},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0.92","g":"0.4","b":"0.3","fadetime":"0.4","block":"true","id":44},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":45},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1394_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":46},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1392_1#1$1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":47},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":48},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1392_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"紧张的阿戈尔人","text":"快看！","id":50},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1394_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的阿戈尔人","text":"——！","id":52},{"type":"charslot","id":53},{"type":"text","text":"那座高耸在城市中央的塔不复存在，取而代之的是某种深海溶洞里才能见到的巨型“石柱”。","id":54},{"type":"text","text":"绵密而多孔的海嗣组织，湿滑而细腻的海嗣组织，层层叠叠地包裹住了信标塔的外墙。","id":55},{"type":"text","text":"但仍有照明设备的灯光从深处透出，将周围的一切晕染得诡异又绮丽。","id":56},{"type":"text","text":"石柱上的菌落簌簌飘落，在广场上展开成造型奇特的生物。","id":57},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1394_1#1$1","focus":"n","id":58},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1392_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"紧张的阿戈尔人","text":"如果不是那几尊雕塑还能看出个大概，我甚至想不到眼前的一切与文明有何关联！","id":60},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1394_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的阿戈尔人","text":"......“巢穴化”。","id":62},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1392_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"紧张的阿戈尔人","text":"城市里怎么会出现海嗣？我们明明都还没有......","id":64},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1394_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的阿戈尔人","text":"只要结果符合预期，过程是不是由我们亲手推动，都无所谓。","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的阿戈尔人","text":"但愿这对于正在沉沦的阿戈尔人来说，会是无法忘记的一课。","id":67},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1392_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"紧张的阿戈尔人","text":"我们现在怎么做？","id":69},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1394_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的阿戈尔人","text":"扩大现有的结果，阻止这座城市进行反击。","id":71},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"n","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"谋害图利娅还不够，你们还要从内部彻底破坏城市？","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我本来还指望再观察一会，顺着你们将其他人一网打尽。","id":74},{"type":"dialog","id":75},{"type":"charslot","id":76},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":77},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":78},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":79},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"事态紧急，收网。","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"你们将是海巡队本月内处理的第三十三、三十四个深海教徒。","id":82},{"type":"charslot","id":83},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1394_1#1$1","focus":"n","id":84},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1392_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"紧张的阿戈尔人","text":"海巡队......","id":86},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1394_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的阿戈尔人","text":"这段时间，你已经伤害了我们太多手足。","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的阿戈尔人","text":"一味地服从既有秩序毫无意义，阿戈尔需要的不是在绝望中苟延残喘——","id":89},{"type":"dialog","id":90},{"type":"charslot","slot":"all","focus":"all","id":91},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":92},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":94},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_seagunshoot","volume":"1","id":95},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":96},{"type":"delay","time":"0.1","id":97},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":98},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":99},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_seagunshoot","volume":"1","id":100},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":101},{"type":"delay","time":"0.4","id":102},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown2","volume":"1","id":103},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"0,-50","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":104},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown2","volume":"1","id":105},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"0,-50","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":106},{"type":"delay","time":"0.4","id":107},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"啰嗦。没时间和你们辩论。","id":109},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"西昆妲指挥官，生物信号异常密集，在短时间内暴涨了三倍。","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"海嗣似乎已经把那座塔筑成了巢穴，它们正在源源不断地从中生成......","id":112},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#6$1","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"不能让这些海嗣向其他城区扩散！","id":114},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"附近的民众已经在自发疏散，你带领一个小队引导大家向避难仓撤离。","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"记得清空路面上的所有辅助机械，如果被海嗣污染，它们会成为对付我们的武器。","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"其他人，结成战斗编队，开启屏障，将海嗣限制在信标塔周边的区域！","id":118},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"明白！","id":120},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"第Ⅳ级武器明明已经启动，难道说......","id":122},{"type":"dialog","id":123},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","style":"slider","inverse":"true","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":125},{"type":"charslot","id":126},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":127},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#9$1","id":128},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","style":"slider","inverse":"true","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":129},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"1","id":130},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"......我在听。","id":132},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#10$1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"立刻封锁第Ⅳ级武器，以最快的速度对武器系统进行全面排查。","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"已经回防的所有队伍立刻在港口枢纽重新集结。","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"从此刻起，所有作战单位保持频道畅通。","id":136},{"type":"dialog","id":137},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":138},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","volume":"1","id":139},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":140},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#4$1","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"......","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"............","id":143},{"type":"dialog","id":144},{"type":"charslot","id":145},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"147","text":"执政官阁下，这和您描述的不太一样。"},"2":{"id":"147","text":"我想，这并不在计划之内吧？"}},"values":[],"id":146},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":147,"end":161},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#5$1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"注意看实时海图。就在一个小时前，海嗣的生物信号整体还趋于稳定。","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"而此刻，大陆架上所有巢穴之间的距离正变得越来越近......不，巢穴本身不会移动，它们只是在无限膨胀。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"就像无数滴浓墨在白纸上晕开。","id":151,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#6$1","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"整片海域都在巢穴化。","id":153},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#6$1","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"点状的巢穴正在连缀成一个整体，而弥利亚留姆，此刻正处于它们的正中间。","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#7$1","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"执政官阁下，阿戈尔投向巢穴的，究竟是驱离海嗣的武器，还是巨量的催化剂？你们究竟在消灭它们，还是喂养它们？","id":157,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#6$1","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"......","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"如果是布兰都斯篡改了信标与武器的联动关系，那么一定也是他的动作扭曲了第Ⅳ级武器的生效方式。","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"就结果而言......","id":161,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":162},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":163},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"165","text":"阿戈尔接触陆地的机会被反向利用了。"},"2":{"id":"165","text":"城市正在变成海嗣向陆地蔓延的据点。"}},"values":[],"id":164},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":165,"end":175},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#9$1","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"作为航道计划的总战争设计师，我会对正在发生的事情负责。但此时此刻，我们还没有输掉这场战役。","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"看看外面，街道上几乎听不见骚乱的动静，弥利亚留姆并未陷入恐慌。","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"在和海嗣纠缠的两百多年间，我们经历过无数次类似的变故。宣布弥利亚留姆失守，还为时尚早。","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"凯尔希医生，博士，现在离开这里，我会保护你们前往港口。","id":170},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我还以为执政官会留守在这里。","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#10$1","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"此时此刻，港口枢纽才是这座城市的心脏，是最不能丢失的阵地。","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"海嗣已经侵入我的城市，我难道要等待这些不速之客敲响这冥思间的门？","id":175,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":176},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":177},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","style":"slider","inverse":"false","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"charslot","id":179},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":180},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#8$1","id":181},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","style":"slider","inverse":"false","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":182},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown3","volume":"0.4","id":183},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#9$1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"0,-20","afrom":"1","ato":"1","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"唔——","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"空气越来越潮湿了，我、我觉得快要喘不上气来......","id":186},{"type":"charslot","id":187},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"注意脚下。用你身上的装置浮起来，不要踩到它。","id":189},{"type":"dialog","id":190},{"type":"charslot","id":191},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_dripink","volume":"0.4","id":192},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_activation","volume":"0.8","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":193},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"1.5","id":194},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#5$1","posfrom":"0,-20","posto":"0,0","afrom":"1","ato":"1","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......溟痕？","id":196},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"溟痕，海嗣的又一种扩张手段。它们已经从塔顶蔓延到了这里，铺开的速度要比陆地上你曾见过的快很多。","id":198},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#6$1","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"海嗣正在城市里筑巢？！","id":200},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"就在我们头顶。","id":202},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#6$1","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"你说有人为海嗣指路......为什么？怎么做到的？","id":204},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#4$1","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"布兰都斯，那个已经死去的人......这就是他五年心血换来的成果。","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"在他可笑的构想里，这座塔发出的信号，以及弥利亚留姆原本用来驱除海嗣的武器，都会成为沟通海嗣与人类的桥梁。","id":207},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"他确实搭建起了某种“桥梁”，只不过海嗣并没有回应他的善意和宏愿。","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"所谓的沟通只是帮这群畜生锁定了弥利亚留姆的位置，理解了它的防御机制。","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"军团费尽心思将这片海域切割成一个个可控的区域，但就在刚刚，所有被分隔的海嗣巢穴顺着信标的信号，重新结为一体。","id":211},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"本应摧毁巢穴、驱除海嗣的第Ⅳ级武器，也发挥了反作用。海嗣的血肉沿着武器打击的路径蔓延，本应凋亡的得到了滋养。","id":213},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#6$1","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......","id":215},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"哼，他至死都没有意识到自己有多傲慢。","id":217},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#2$1","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"乌尔比安阁下，我不太听得懂您在说什么。但眼下......","id":219},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"这座塔已经被海嗣视作新的巢穴，它会源源不断地吐出幼体，也会吸引其他巢穴的海嗣向此处聚集。","id":221},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#6$1","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我们能阻止这种变化吗？","id":223},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"来不及了。","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我们唯一还来得及做的，是将信标塔所在的城市单元切割出去。","id":226},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#5$1","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......切割？","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"可水下城市又不是积木搭起来的，要怎么做才能......","id":229},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你对阿戈尔的了解还是太少。","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"和那些由笨重地块拼起来的陆上移动城市不同，阿戈尔的科技更注重生物性，这一点在城市建设上体现得尤为明显。","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"对一只受伤的海兽来说，咬断自己中毒的肢体，只是本能的反应，而且不算什么难事。","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我们必须保住这座城市的剩余部分，它还有用。否则，当整片海域的海嗣都连成狂潮，再没有什么能够阻挡它们。","id":234},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#4$1","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"海嗣会毫无阻拦地冲上陆地，冲进......伊比利亚......","id":236},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#6$1","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"乌尔比安阁下，具体该怎么做？","id":238},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"庞大而精密的骨架支撑着弥利亚留姆的各个城市单元。控制信标塔所在单元的联动装置操作系统，应该就在这个中控室里。","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"启用它，让整座信标塔沉入海底。","id":241},{"type":"dialog","id":242},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":243},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":244},{"type":"charslot","id":245},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":246},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":247},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":248},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":249},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......是这个吗？","id":251},{"type":"dialog","id":252},{"type":"playsound","key":"$keyboard","volume":"1","id":253},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":254},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_button","volume":"1","id":255},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":256},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#8$1","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我能操作——但为什么没有任何反应？","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"看起来操作系统没有问题，那就是联动装置本身......","id":259},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"设施管理所有专人负责城市单元骨架的检查与维护，它发生故障的概率比深海猎人武器生锈的概率还要低。","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"偏偏是这个时间，这个地点......","id":262},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#8$1","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......","id":264},{"type":"dialog","id":265},{"type":"playsound","key":"$flashback","volume":"0.8","id":266},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":267},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":268},{"type":"charslot","id":269},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":270},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":271},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1401_1#1$1","id":272},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_microrobot","volume":"1","id":273},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"设施管理所的“小帮手”","text":"读数误差，第二次报错。","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"设施管理所的“小帮手”","text":"是否运行故障测试？","id":276},{"type":"charslot","id":277},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"......","id":279},{"type":"dialog","id":280},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":281},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":282},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","id":283},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":284},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"阿维图斯先生，需要我帮您吗？","id":286},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"不，不用。我只是在观察这台被人抛下的小帮手。","id":288},{"type":"dialog","id":289},{"type":"playsound","key":"$flashback","volume":"0.8","id":290},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":291},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":292},{"type":"charslot","id":293},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":294},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#4$1","id":295},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0","keep":"true","id":296},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"难道......","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"他真的知道些什么？","id":300},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#7$1","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"嗯？","id":302},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#6$1","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"乌尔比安先生，或许，我知道应该去找谁了。","id":304},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"联系外面的阿戈尔军人，他们会接应你离开这里。","id":307},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#5$1","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"您要一个人留在这里？","id":310},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#7$1","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"年轻人，你仍然对我保持怀疑，很好。","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"但必须有人留在中控室。","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"一旦信标塔完全变成巢穴，哪怕我们修好了联动装置，弥利亚留姆也无法切割掉这里——","id":314},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#4$1","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"海兽无法吐出那颗不再属于它的心脏。","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我必须守在这里，亲眼确认城市单元骨架恢复运作，亲手将信标塔切割出去。","id":317},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#8$1","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"可是这样的话......您会和信标塔一起沉入海底，您会被无穷无尽的海嗣包围，直到......","id":319},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#7$1","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"这不需要你来担心。还是说，你觉得自己比我更适合做这件事情？","id":321},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#8$1","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......","id":323},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#2$1","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你的时间不多了，年轻人。","id":325},{"type":"dialog","id":326},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":327},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"1","id":328},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":329},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#5$1","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"您、您怎么已经......","id":331},{"type":"charslot","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"信标塔的频道？","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"海巡队，西昆妲。谁在信标塔内？","id":334},{"type":"dialog","id":335},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":336},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","style":"slider","inverse":"true","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":337},{"type":"charslot","id":338},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":339},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":340},{"type":"interlude","maskid":"group_interclude_vertical_common","size":"290,760","style":"0","switch":"true","offset":"250,0","channel":"3","tsfrom":"0,1","tsto":"1,1","tsduration":"0","id":341},{"type":"3","channel":"3","slot":"m","switch":"false","pfrom":"250,0","pto":"250,0","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","duration":"0","id":342},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":343},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","style":"slider","inverse":"true","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"那布兰都斯？","id":345},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"n","id":346},{"type":"3","channel":"3","slot":"m","pfrom":"250,0","pto":"250,0","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","duration":"0","switch":"true","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"已经死了。","id":348},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#2$1","id":349},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"false","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"......","id":351},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我与他一直保持着往来，却没能及时发现异样，事后我应该向执政官领受责罚。","id":353},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"n","id":354},{"type":"3","channel":"3","switch":"true","slot":"m","pfrom":"250,0","pto":"250,0","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","duration":"0","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"弥利亚留姆需要丢弃这座塔，而我必须亲眼看着它沉入海底。","id":356},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":357},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"false","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"在那之后呢？","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"你是否还会，又是否还能回到阿戈尔？","id":360},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"n","id":361},{"type":"3","channel":"3","switch":"true","slot":"m","pfrom":"250,0","pto":"250,0","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","duration":"0","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"不要提无效的问题，西昆妲。","id":363},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你不应因过往而优柔寡断。","id":364},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":365},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"false","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"......乌尔比安，你想多了。","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"布兰都斯告诉了我当年的事情。","id":368},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"不管驳回我申请的人是你，还是布兰都斯，对我来说都没有区别。","id":369},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#10$1","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"或许我应该承认......没能成为深海猎人，没能和你们并肩作战，对我而言——非常遗憾，非常。","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我承认当时我有过很长时间的愤怒与不满......我甚至有些嫉妒斯卡蒂。","id":372},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"但后来，我习惯了为你们巡航，为一切守护我们家园和文明的计划巡航。","id":374},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"n","id":375},{"type":"3","channel":"3","switch":"true","slot":"m","pfrom":"250,0","pto":"250,0","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#2$1","duration":"0","id":376},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"置身于任何一项具体的计划之外，会让你看到更多的牺牲，更多的背叛，更多值得怀疑的人，更多脱离轨道的事。","id":377},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","id":378},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"false","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"就像现在的你一样？","id":380},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"n","id":381},{"type":"3","channel":"3","switch":"true","slot":"m","pfrom":"250,0","pto":"250,0","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#4$1","duration":"0","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":383},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你想好你该背负的了？","id":384},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","id":385},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"false","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"如果你确实背叛了阿戈尔，真的与那群渣滓为伍，那么你此刻留在信标塔即是为了逃离，我会承担放走一位堕落者的罪责。","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"如果你仍是深海猎人，你将孤身战斗......但潜入城市、突入信标塔，加上评议会的结果，你的嫌疑已经很难洗清。","id":388},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#2$1","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"阿戈尔或许不会铭记你的牺牲......就像图利娅注定会被遗忘。","id":390},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"但此时切割信标塔，确实能在最大程度上帮助弥利亚留姆应对灾变。","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我认同你的选择，我会给予你最低程度的信任。","id":393},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"n","id":394},{"type":"3","channel":"3","switch":"true","slot":"m","pfrom":"250,0","pto":"250,0","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#4$1","duration":"0","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"哼......嗯。","id":396},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"false","id":397},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"五分钟。五分钟后我会接应那个陆地人离开信标塔。","id":399},{"type":"dialog","id":400},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":401},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":402},{"type":"charslot","id":403},{"type":"interlude","clear":"true","id":404},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":405},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":406},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":407},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#9$1","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"全城已经启动应急交通协调预案，我们接下来会从斗智场驶入中轴通道，前往港口枢纽。","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"我会留在港口枢纽指挥作战，海巡队会接管这艘舰船，护送你们尽快返回陆地。","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"无人机矩阵也将前往那座灯塔，协助伊比利亚完成布防。","id":411},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":412},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"弥利亚留姆是否也应该组织城内的民众撤离？","id":413,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#9$1","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"弥利亚留姆是一座军事堡垒，它具备在战时安置民众的能力。与战斗无关的民众已经在海巡队的护送下前往避难仓。","id":415},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#6$1","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"——","id":417},{"type":"dialog","id":418},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":419},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"421","text":"执政官阁下，您手边的那些神经缆线......"}},"values":[],"id":420},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":421},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"423","text":"不应该以这种扭曲的方式抽搐吧？"}},"values":[],"id":422},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":423,"end":427},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#6$1","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"不应该。通讯失灵了，我与舰船操作系统的连接也被切断了......我正在失去对舰船的控制。","id":425},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#10$1","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"小帮手，立刻运行全舰检测程序。","id":427,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":428},{"type":"charslot","id":429},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_microrobot","volume":"1","id":430},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1401_1#1$1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“小帮手”","text":"——","id":432},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#10$1","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"系统被入侵的程度比我刚刚预想的还要严重。","id":434},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"两位，非常抱歉，我们可能来不及降落了。","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"弥利亚留姆城内的人工重力环境还没有失效，你们身上的装置可以帮助你们在空中自由游动。","id":436},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"跟着我，不必害怕，从舱门走出去就可以。","id":437},{"type":"dialog","id":438},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_higheldshosfts","volume":"1","id":439},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":440},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_glassdooropen","volume":"1","id":441},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":442},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":443},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":444},{"type":"charslot","id":445},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","id":446},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":447},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"6","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"90","randomness":"50","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":448},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_collapse","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"b","id":449},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":450},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"b","fadetime":"4","id":451},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":452},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#9$1","id":453},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"通讯依然没有恢复，整个斗智场似乎被谁以某种手段与外界隔绝了。","id":454},{"type":"dialog","id":455},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_brainnucleiturn","volume":"0.4","id":456},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":457},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#11$1","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"——","id":459},{"type":"charslot","id":460},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":461},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#7$1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"150,0","duration":"0","id":462},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"——Mon3tr！","id":463,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":464},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fireburst","volume":"1","id":465},{"type":"backgroundtween","xFrom":"0","xTo":"-65","duration":"1","ease":"OutQuad","block":"false","id":466},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#7$1","posfrom":"150,0","posto":"0,0","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","id":467},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":468},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_skill_Mon3trburst","volume":"0.4","id":469},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"npc_10002","afrom":"0","ato":"1","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":470},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mon3tr","text":"（警惕的啸叫）","id":471,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_npc_10002_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":472},{"type":"text","text":"Mon3tr张开漆黑的利爪，灼热感扑面而来。执政官也几乎同时做出了反应，她拔出仪仗剑，侧身挡在你与凯尔希的身前。","id":473},{"type":"text","text":"你们同时留意到了前方的“敌人”。","id":474},{"type":"dialog","id":475},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":476},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":477},{"type":"charslot","id":478},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_seabornbacklair","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"u","id":479},{"type":"playmusic","volume":"0.6","id":480,"musicid":1},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.5","yScale":"1.5","y":"-100","fadetime":"2","id":481},{"type":"backgroundtween","yFrom":"-30","yTo":"30","duration":"8","block":"false","id":482},{"type":"bg","id":483,"from":"0","to":"1","duration":"0.1","block":"false"},{"type":"curtain","direction":"2","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"0.2","fadetime":"0.1","id":484},{"type":"curtain","direction":"6","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"0.6","fadetime":"0.1","id":485},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1383_1#1$1","posfrom":"-60,20","posto":"-60,-20","afrom":"1","ato":"1","duration":"3.7","id":486},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"zoom","poszoom":"0.5,0.5","scale":"1.3","duration":"0","id":487},{"type":"delay","time":"0.1","id":488},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":489},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":490},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":491},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":492},{"type":"charslot","id":493},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.5","yScale":"1.5","fadetime":"2","id":494},{"type":"backgroundtween","yFrom":"0","yTo":"60","duration":"8","block":"false","id":495},{"type":"bg","id":496,"from":"0","to":"1","duration":"0.1","block":"false"},{"type":"curtain","direction":"2","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"0.6","fadetime":"0.1","id":497},{"type":"curtain","direction":"6","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"0.2","fadetime":"0.1","id":498},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1383_1#1$1","posfrom":"60,20","posto":"60,-20","afrom":"1","ato":"1","duration":"3.7","id":499},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"zoom","poszoom":"0.5,0.5","scale":"1.3","duration":"0","id":500},{"type":"delay","time":"0.1","id":501},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":502},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":503},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":504},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":505},{"type":"curtain","id":506},{"type":"charslot","id":507},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","y":"-50","fadetime":"2","id":508},{"type":"backgroundtween","yFrom":"-50","yTo":"0","duration":"6","id":509},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"u","fadetime":"4","id":510},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_brainnucleiturn","volume":"1","id":511},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1383_1#1$1","posfrom":"0,50","posto":"0,0","duration":"6","id":512},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"zoom","poszoom":"0.5,0.5","scale":"1","duration":"0","id":513},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":514},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":515},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......","id":516},{"type":"text","text":"一只形貌特殊的海嗣悬在你们面前。","id":517},{"type":"text","text":"它似乎没有敌意，在被Mon3tr的叫声惊动之前，它只是安静地悬在那里，斗智场中央的珊瑚状终端照亮它没有五官的脸。","id":518},{"type":"text","text":"环绕在海嗣身体周围的粒状细胞器如同手臂般展开，“摩挲”着枝叶，与上面那些流动的文字与符号融为一体。","id":519},{"type":"text","text":"它在观察？它在感受？它能理解那些属于人类的感性和理性吗？","id":520},{"type":"dialog","id":521},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_underwtr","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"u","id":522},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"u","fadetime":"4","id":523},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"3","id":524},{"type":"bg","id":525,"from":"1","to":"0","duration":"3","block":"false"},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":526},{"type":"text","text":"它转向了你们。","id":527},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#11$1","id":528},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"一只......海嗣。是它入侵了斗智场的终端？前所未见的能力，这不是什么好现象。","id":529},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1383_1#1$1","id":530},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的海嗣","text":"（模糊的阿戈尔语）此处并无正义，唯有前路。","id":531},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#10$1","id":532},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"一只海嗣侵入阿戈尔的城市，在先哲设计的圣地念诵古老的箴言。","id":533},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"这是我参与这场战争以来，见过的最为讽刺的画面、最为无礼的挑衅。","id":534},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#6$1","id":535},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"它对语言的运用，说话的方式和习惯......并非海嗣强行“学习”的结果。","id":536,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"执政官阁下，这只海嗣恐怕曾是人类。","id":537,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1383_1#1$1","id":538},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的海嗣","text":"语言。我从未将它遗忘，而它也不曾弃我而去。","id":539},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#10$1","id":540},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"那么你的思想呢？你拙劣地模仿先哲的话语时，是否理解自己所念诵的言辞？","id":541},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1383_1#3$1","id":542},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的海嗣","text":"理解？不。留下这句话的时候，我并不理解它真正的含义。","id":543},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的海嗣","text":"如今，我重新认知。","id":544},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#7$1","id":545},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"留下这句话......玛利图斯？","id":546},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"......你？！","id":547},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#10$1","id":548},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"地幔遗迹第四考察队的核心成员，两百多年前意外失踪的人类学家暨先史文明研究者，玛利图斯？","id":549},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1383_1#3$1","id":550},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的海嗣","text":"......十分遥远的回忆，我确实，曾被如此称呼。","id":551},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1383_1#1$1","id":552},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的海嗣","text":"但如今，你只需理解现象本身。你们面前是一只海嗣。你们只需要如此称呼我。","id":553},{"type":"dialogue","name":"神秘的海嗣","text":"“海嗣”。","id":554},{"type":"charslot","id":555},{"type":"text","text":"海嗣飘向了你们。","id":556},{"type":"text","text":"透过它透明的颅腔，你看见色泽诡异的核状物聚拢又散开，稳定地变化着。","id":557},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1383_1#1$1","id":558},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“海嗣”","text":"阿戈尔人，现在，让我和你身后的人谈谈。","id":559},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":560},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_skill_Mon3trburst","volume":"0.4","id":561},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"npc_10002","id":562},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mon3tr","text":"（愤怒的吼叫）","id":563,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_npc_10002_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1383_1#1$1","id":564},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“海嗣”","text":"咕——让这个小东西收起獠牙吧，它的火焰无法烧灼我的血液。","id":565},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“海嗣”","text":"AMa-10——","id":566},{"type":"dialog","id":567},{"type":"charslot","id":568},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"570","text":"你是谁？你为什么这么称呼凯尔希？"},"2":{"id":"570","text":"你知道凯尔希的身份？"}},"values":[],"id":569},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":570,"end":576},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#6$1","id":571},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":572,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"Dr.{@nickname}，保持警惕。我来与它对话。","id":573,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1383_1#2$1","id":574},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“海嗣”","text":"Kal-tsit......凯尔希。原来如此。如果你更习惯被称作凯尔希，那我也可以如此称呼你——","id":575},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“海嗣”","text":"凯尔希，我等待你，你们，很长时间。","id":576,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":577},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":578},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":579},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":580},{"type":"charslot","id":581},{"type":"background","id":582},{"type":"image","id":583}],"characters":["紧张的阿戈尔人","神秘的阿戈尔人","？？？","西昆妲","海巡队队长","克莱门莎","凯尔希","乔迪","乌尔比安","设施管理所的“小帮手”","阿维图斯","“小帮手”","Mon3tr","神秘的海嗣","“海嗣”"]}